---
title: "Hotwire & Tailwind Demo"
layout: application
---

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-8">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-8">Sitepress with Hotwire & Tailwind</h1>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    <!-- Turbo Demo -->
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">🚀 Turbo Navigation</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Turbo provides fast navigation between pages without full page reloads.</p>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <a href="/hi.html" class="block bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors">
          Navigate to Hi Page (Turbo)
        </a>
        <a href="/time.html" class="block bg-green-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors">
          Navigate to Time Page (Turbo)
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stimulus Demo -->
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg" data-controller="hello">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">⚡ Stimulus Interactivity</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Stimulus provides JavaScript behavior for your pages.</p>
      <button 
        data-action="click->hello#greet" 
        class="bg-purple-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-purple-600 transition-colors mb-4"
      >
        Click me!
      </button>
      <div data-hello-target="output" class="text-lg font-medium text-purple-600"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tailwind Demo -->
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">🎨 Tailwind CSS</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Beautiful, responsive design with utility-first CSS.</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
        <div class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 p-2 text-center rounded">Red</div>
        <div class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 p-2 text-center rounded">Green</div>
        <div class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 p-2 text-center rounded">Blue</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Combined Demo -->
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg" data-controller="counter">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">🔥 All Together</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Turbo + Stimulus + Tailwind working in harmony.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
        <button 
          data-action="click->counter#increment" 
          class="bg-indigo-500 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded hover:bg-indigo-600 transition-colors"
        >
          +
        </button>
        <span data-counter-target="count" class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600">0</span>
        <button 
          data-action="click->counter#decrement"
          class="bg-indigo-500 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded hover:bg-indigo-600 transition-colors"
        >
          -
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">✅ What's Working</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
        Hotwire Turbo for fast navigation
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
        Stimulus for JavaScript behavior
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
        Tailwind CSS for styling
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
        No build tools required
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
        Importmaps for module loading
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>